summary: This is an email correspondence from an unidentified sender to an unidentified recipient regarding a response from JPMorgan Chase to a subpoena related to case EFTA00151211. The email includes attachments containing the response letter, the subpoena, and three Excel files of wire transfer data.

events.title: Email regarding Chase subpoena response
events.description: An email is sent containing attachments from JPMorgan Chase in response to a subpoena for case EFTA00151211, including wire transfer data.

keyFacts: JPMorgan Chase provided a response to a subpoena for case EFTA00151211.
The response included a letter, the subpoena, and three Excel files containing wire transfer data.
The document is an email dated September 25, 2019, indicating ongoing legal discovery or investigation.
The file references (WIRES_0975.xlsx, WIRES_9001.xlsx, WIRES_9065.xlsx) suggest financial transaction records were subpoenaed.
The case identifier EFTA00151211 is central to the document.
